<input type="checkbox" id="hypBox" class="tenseBox"> <label for="hypBox">Hypothetical tense</label><br>
<input type="number" id="minTenses" min=1 max=[tenseCh] value=1 oninput="minTenses = Number(this.value)"> Minimum tenses<br>
<input type="number" id="maxTenses" min=1 max=[tenseCh] value=3 oninput="maxTenses = Number(this.value)"> Maximum tenses

<p>Due to technical limitations, you must press the "randomise" button before changes to the min or max tenses will update.</p>
<p>Genuinely sorry about that, will work on a fix.</p>
<p>Also it seems that on some devices you may be able to select a minimum or maximum higher than the amount of tenses you're permitting with the checkboxes. This'll cause the generator to use tenses you've not permitted.</p>

</details>

